description: Developed by the luxury marque’s new performance brand, AMR. Making its public debut at the 2017 Goodwood Festival of Speed, the Aston Martin Vulcan AMR Pro sports extensive aerodynamic enhancements and shortened gearing to produce increased downforce, greater responsiveness and reduced lap times – improvements that underline its status as one of the world’s most extreme and exclusive track cars.
creator: Bnuuy
